name: RCNZ Orangutan With A Plan
description:
Following on from Dumb Monkey and Gorilla With A Brick, I've taken the best of the Stable Diffusion 2 models available, and merged them to create another randomly usable model!

There is no VAE baked in as I didn't think it was necessary. Both ckpt and safetensor versions are fp16
